author: Sam Dorman
title: Ted Cruz praises Bill Maher for 'rant' about coronavirus originating in China
description: Sen. Ted Cruz, R-Texas, reached across the aisle Saturday when he praised comedian Bill Maher for his monologue panning liberals over their concerns about the term "Chinese virus."
content:
